### Test PolicyAccount với OwnerName field

### 1. Tạo account với OwnerName
POST https://localhost:7001/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "policyNumber": "POL100",
    "policyAccountNumber": "ACC100",
    "ownerName": "Nguyen Minh Khanh",
    "balance": 10000.00
}

### 2. Tạo account khác với OwnerName
POST https://localhost:7001/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "policyNumber": "POL101", 
    "policyAccountNumber": "ACC101",
    "ownerName": "Tran Van Nam",
    "balance": 5500.75
}

### 3. Tìm account đầu tiên - sẽ trả về với OwnerName
GET https://localhost:7001/api/account/POL100

### 4. Tìm account thứ hai - sẽ trả về với OwnerName  
GET https://localhost:7001/api/account/POL101

### 5. Test với Minimal API
POST https://localhost:7001/policy-accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "policyNumber": "POL102",
    "policyAccountNumber": "ACC102", 
    "ownerName": "Le Thi Hoa",
    "balance": 7500.50
}

### 6. Tìm account qua Minimal API
GET https://localhost:7001/policy-accounts/POL102